{"tid":1381420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"物資鏈組人入黎睇！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:06:37.000Z","uid":293486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdea8791062c7a98f81feb509be5de0130243543","tid":1381420,"uid":293486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"(之前友人代出，終於申請到P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，自己重POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n物資鏈分析<br />\n<br />\n物資鏈輸送既效率直接影響前線手兄既安危，出呢篇野亦係希望可以減少前線手足要抽大量人手去控制條鏈，有少少經驗同建議希望大家可以參考跟一跟，認同希望推下，有建議盡量打，屌細力啲！<br />\n<br />\n1. 吾好企甘密！吾好企甘密！吾好企甘密！一個正常人，攤開手，兩邊都剛剛好掂吾到人既距離係最想，亦都係傳野最快既速度！人多係無用，要快，要效率！<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人叫物資鏈既時候，大家醒水做兩條鏈，中間留大約 2 米距離做快線，兩條主鏈後面要絲打BACKUP，巴打負責第一排傳野，絲打企後一排負責隨時開傘 COVER 快線手足，同時睇住前排需要乜！合作好緊要！！<br />\n<br />\n3. 拆包裝！拆包裝！拆包裝！<br />\n傳緊既巴打拆吾切，比後排絲打拆左再繼續傳！<br />\n<br />\n4. 分類<br />\n第一優先：頭盔、眼罩、豬嘴、盾，見到呢啲除非叫停，吾係通常都會要<br />\n第二優先：長傘、索帶、剪刀或士巴拿，水，空樽等，準備定，要就傳，無就放係後排，前線太多野要走都好難走！<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果前線無左，中後線都會無，所以各位手足，請請請將你地身上既物資捐俾前線！1 億個吾該！<br />\n<br />\n利申，自己細撚膽，一直以黎都係玩緊中後排既角色，堅守齊上齊落，不分，不割！我係香港人！"},{"pid":"dcfd928a7e0976b7706bf075abeebddcb334531b","tid":1381420,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:35:02.000Z","msg":"推晒所有戰術post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［重開 長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb552aa01eb2e88536631629c929841e5711b90d","tid":1381420,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"721d5a0d20c3c1c62cb4ac56fdf9f80996e755c9","tid":1381420,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港  時代革命"},{"pid":"6513c3333392d3d9ca0bc106fd250a1204e5f745","tid":1381420,"uid":293486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19050d61c3e1353d2acc5c1cde05e9a2dfc08821","tid":1381420,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMV3tnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMV3tnr.png&h=77fc1786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Rgez2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Rgez2q.png&h=b86a56fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgkSmHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgkSmHq.jpg&h=d447c2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY6Vjt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY6Vjt5.jpg&h=18989aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLe7U2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLe7U2r.jpg&h=98c959ff&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}